Package org.jnosql.diana.api.reader

The ValueReader has the goal read a information from Value by Class informed from Value.get(java.lang.Class).

See: Description

Package org.jnosql.diana.api.reader Description

The ValueReader has the goal read a information from Value by Class informed from Value.get(java.lang.Class). This package has all implementations supported by default in Diana Project
